This repository contains all the codes and other documents related to the manuscript Ribeiro et al 2024.

PROTOCOLS
Compressed file "1.Protocols.zip" (Link to HCR protocol) 

R CODES, DATA ANALYSIS INPUT AND OUTPUTS
Compressed files 2-4:
"2.Experiments_log.zip" 	(link)	
"3.RNAseq_analysis_dataset.zip" (link)
"4.RT-PCR_data.zip" (link)
"5.Sex_ratio_data.zip" (link)
Consider: Spreadsheets (.csv, .xlsx files), associated R codes, and summarized results in .pptx format are combined into compressed files. Each compressed file includes a .txt file titled "Description of Files," which explains their contents.

ADDITIONAL ASSOCIATED DATA

SEQUENCING DATA
RNAseq raw reads are available under XXXX (SRA/NCBI)
Gene sequences (mRNA) are available under XXXX (GENBANK/ NCBI)

IMAGING DATA AND TRANSCRIPTOME ASSEMBLIES
We have uploaded transcriptome assemblies and the original imaging files to Zenodo: https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.11619572. 
Information on the hairpins and probe sets used for HCR in situ hybridizations has also been added to the Zenodo repository alongside the imaging data.




